- '72 Ferrari, yeah.
- But,

56
00:02:08,476 --> 00:02:10,340
And you sweep me off my feet.

57
00:02:10,687 --> 00:02:12,390
And I liked it.

58
00:02:12,648 --> 00:02:14,913
That's good 'cause
I wasn't sure you would.

59
00:02:15,296 --> 00:02:18,780
