93
00:04:00,869 --> 00:04:02,596
It's... it's about the baby.

94
00:04:02,705 --> 00:04:04,564
♪♪

95
00:04:04,875 --> 00:04:07,304
I'm just worried
I'll never be a father.

96
00:04:07,465 --> 00:04:11,267
