197
00:08:22,326 --> 00:08:24,947
the world to know there was
a new sheriff in town,

198
00:08:25,096 --> 00:08:26,962
and the message that sends
isn't that you have

199
00:08:27,017 --> 00:08:30,587
something to prove...
